	abstract = {Using a cosmological N-body simulation and a sample of resimulated 
cluster-like haloes, we study the mass-loss rates of dark matter
subhaloes, and interpret the mass function of subhaloes at redshift zero
in terms of the evolution of the mass function of systems accreted by
