	url = {http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1979ApJS...41..555H},
	abstract = {The paper analyzes the structure of fast shocks incident upon
interstellar gas of ambient density from 10 to the 7th per cu cm, while
focusing on the problems of formation and destruction of molecules and
infrared emission in the cooling, neutral post shock gas. It is noted
that such fast shocks initially dissociate almost all preexisting
