	abstract = {We present measurements of the stellar mass functions ({SMFs}) of 
star-forming and quiescent galaxies to z = 4 using a sample of 95,675
Ks -selected galaxies in the {COSMOS}/{UltraVISTA} field. The
{SMFs} of the combined population are in good agreement with previous
